Class PropertyContext

java.lang.Object
  name.pehl.piriti.rebind.LogFacade
      name.pehl.piriti.rebind.PropertyContext

public class PropertyContext
extends LogFacade

Class which contains information needed to generate code for the evaluation, conversion and assignment of one property. An instance of this class is passed to the PropertyHandler.
